Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,E-E-Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:09.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,X791, Port Hargeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:13.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven years have passed \Nsince Natsu and the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:17.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,disappeared without a trace \Nfrom Tenroujima Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.80,0:00:21.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you gonna stare at the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:23.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our work is finished, so \Nlet's get back to the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:28.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.04,0:00:32.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you aren't back soon, your dad will worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:38.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This man is Fairy Tail's Alzack Connell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:42.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This woman is Bisca Connell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.61,0:00:46.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Macao asked us to take care of you, Romeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.54,0:00:48.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.43,0:00:53.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And this boy is Romeo Conbolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:57.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Romeo... I know how you feel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.31,0:00:58.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bisca...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.81,0:01:07.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-nii...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.11,0:02:42.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Magnolia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:46.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't changed in the past seven \Nyears and is as thriving as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:54.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And standing quietly on a hillside \Nfar from the the heart of the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:09.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail, X791!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.45,0:03:13.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Romeo isn't home yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:18.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Al and Bisca ditched \Nhim and went off to snuggle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:20.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, pipe down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:23.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too old for these outbursts, \Nso take it easy, Macao.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:28.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to call me Master, Wakaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:33.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a master with less dignity \Nthan you! 4th Guild Master, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:37.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You do realize you're supposed \Nto be the master's advisor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:39.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have we been losing members again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:45.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:49.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't give the good jobs \Nto a minor guild like ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:52.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Warren, just look at how few jobs there are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:54.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:57.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't been out on a \Njob in seven years, Nab!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:03:59.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:02.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Visitar Ecor has completed his new dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:04.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I call it the Puny Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:07.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It disgusts me, so get him out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:10.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinana-chan, bring me another one of these!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:11.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:15.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Droy, are you putting more \Nstress on the ground these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:17.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You trying to say I got fatter, wench?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:21.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take it out on Laki. And \Ndon't you have any self-awareness?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:24.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at Reedus! See how slim he's gotten?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:28.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oui. This is my true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:30.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been in training!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:32.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell from these muscles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.65,0:04:35.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And see how ladylike Kinana has become!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:36.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to her, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:40.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'm trying to increase \Nmy magic power by eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:41.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:46.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. What would Levy say \Nif she could see you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:49.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy's not coming home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:04.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oui...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:07.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:12.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As always, this place is dead \Nfrom the afternoon on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:14.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I hate about pissant guilds!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:18.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no spirit here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.87,0:05:19.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Teebo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:22.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to stay away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:26.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey. Is that any way to talk to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:32.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Members of Magnolia's number one \Nwizard guild, Twilight Ogre?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:41.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You may once have been the strongest \Nguild in Fiore, but that era is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:44.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Between this ramshackle old \Ntavern and Twilight Ogre,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:48.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the wizard guild of the new \Nage, one glance is all it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:53.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to tell which is more useful to the \Ndevelopment and progress of Magnolia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:57.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Acting big just because \Nyou've got a huge guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:06:00.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! We've got soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:03.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul doesn't put food on the plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:06.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you come here for, Teebo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:09.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This month's money!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:12.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't pay them yet, Macao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:14.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Master, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.51,0:06:19.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You people are late repaying your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:22.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't get any decent jobs this month!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:25.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you double next \Nmonth, so just be patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:30.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa. Who was it that \Nsaved this beat-up tavern
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:31.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,when it was on the brink of collapse?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:36.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We took on your debt for you, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:38.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And if we knew how ridiculously \Nhigh the interest was gonna be,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:41.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we never would've turned to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something, asswipe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:46.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:46.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:52.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait 'til next month, and I promise I'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:57.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Macao!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:57.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:01.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way across the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:04.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He did a first-rate job of flyin' backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:06.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:07.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:09.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You want a go at us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:11.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:18.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard the man. Suck it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:23.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:25.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the legendary Fairy Tail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:26.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Way lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:31.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about joinin' us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:39.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was good for a laugh. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:40.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:44.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you forget. Next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:46.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:16.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oui...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:57.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been seven years, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That long?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:02.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm feelin' nostalgic...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:06.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's changed since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:10.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When we heard that Tenroujima was destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:12.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we searched for everyone \Ndesperately, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:15.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we didn't find even one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:22.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If what the Council said is true, \NAcnologia vaporized the whole island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:30.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Various groups helped us search for \Nthem, but not a single clue was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:32.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:36.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An abnormal concentration of Ethernano
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:38.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,was recorded in the sea \Naround Tenroujima that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:42.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A level that no living thing could survive, \Nlet alone retain their structure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:46.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Acnologia's roar is that powerful?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:52.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, that's the dragon said to have \Ndestroyed an entire country by itself long ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:56.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way humans can face \Nan enemy like that and live...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:01.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did our comrades have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:09.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our guild's weakened \Nsince they disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:13.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, a new guild has \Nbeen established in Magnolia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.00,0:10:17.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's time to close up shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:19.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:23.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Macao?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:25.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:29.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think my heart is gonna break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:36.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been doing a good job... Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:38.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:45.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Romeo hasn't smiled once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:00.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:01.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:04.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Has Ogre come back to harass us some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.09,0:11:10.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:15.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Pegasus'... Christina Ver. 2?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:22.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:25.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:30.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No good... No... A depressing \Nparfum is no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:32.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A youkai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:34.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:35.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:37.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He jumped!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:39.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Twinkling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.17,0:11:43.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:45.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He fell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:47.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:52.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Ichya has arrived...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:58.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This man is Blue Pegasus' \NIchiya Vandalay Kotobuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:11:59.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:05.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichiya-sama, I know how you feel, but \Nmaybe you should calm down a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:08.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I use Air Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:09.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:11.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:12.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:15.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ren!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:18.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Macao-san, have you aged again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:19.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eve!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:23.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Blue Pegasus! They're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:25.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world are they here for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:28.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laki-san, you're as beautiful as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:30.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You look {\i1}too{\i0} good in glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:32.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I call you "Onee-chan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:34.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna pick up a girl, do it elsewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:40.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinana-san, are you free tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:42.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That dress looks {\i1}too{\i0} good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:45.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided! I'm gonna \Nbe your little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:47.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:49.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did you come here for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:53.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! Gentlemen, we're \Nnot here to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:55.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:57.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ichiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:12:58.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:12:59.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:06.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never forget the parfum of friendship \Nof those I've fought alongside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:09.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was worth using Archive's \Ninformation analysis
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:15.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and Christina's mobility to \Ninvestigate Fiore's Ethernano level.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:22.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenroujima... still exists!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:54.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really in this area?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:56.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:13:59.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the Pegasus guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.34,0:14:02.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,there's something about Ethernano \Nin this part of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:05.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Ethernano in the first place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:08.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I know! Something to \Ndo with magic molecules...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:11.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about telepathic communication?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:13.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not picking up anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:18.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Are you sure we shouldn't \Nhave brought Romeo along?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:20.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should have forced him to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:24.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no guarantee that \Neveryone is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:28.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right? Getting him excited \Nprematurely wouldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:31.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:32.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We get to see Levy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:34.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The poster boys for getting \Nexcited prematurely...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:36.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The team, Shadow Gear, together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:36.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how they feel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:39.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:41.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't had any contact for seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:44.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the worst case scenario in mind, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:46.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:52.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:54.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.09,0:14:55.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind's stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:59.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, \Nit is strangely quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:00.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any birds...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:02.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.35,0:15:10.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:11.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A person?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:12.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:14.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's over the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:17.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Look closely at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:22.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She's standing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:24.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:49.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:08.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Al! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:09.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:16.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenroujima!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:17.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tenroujima!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:42.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl! She went to Tenroujima!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:43.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow her! Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:45.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:46.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:52.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:54.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:56.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:17:00.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but she did \Nshow us where Tenroujima is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:03.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she'll lead us to everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:04.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good point!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:06.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose sight of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:07.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:08.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:17.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange... Where did the girl go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:24.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:25.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:26.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:28.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you just standing there for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:43.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.78,0:17:53.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Romeo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:54.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you didn't wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:18:01.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they do find Tenroujima... \Nwho knows if everyone is still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:05.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that! You need to have faith!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:07.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't heard from them in seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:17.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well... Looks like there are \Neven less people in here than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:20.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a guild so \Nmuch as a, what? A club?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:22.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Teebo! We agreed that I'd pay you next month!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:26.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My master doesn't agree with those terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:33.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He said payments have to be made when \Nthey're due. Nothing I can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:36.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can all go to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:37.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Romeo, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:40.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have the money to pay you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:42.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like your attitude, you little brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:44.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Letting punks like you walk all over us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:46.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad and everyone else are cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:49.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:52.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause at this rate, Fairy \NTail's name will be disgraced!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:53.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Romeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:54.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:57.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That name's been dragged \Nthrough the mud long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:18:59.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:05.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You assholes will never make it back \Nup to our level as long as you live!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:18.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:33.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:35.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it took us so long, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:38.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this tiny guild?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:40.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:41.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all so young!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:44.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed in seven years!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:46.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:47.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:51.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu! Wake up! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:53.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Open your eyes, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:55.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:56.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:00.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is goin' on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:02.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doin' here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:04.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And have you aged some?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:06.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:08.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Droy, you got fa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:12.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is it morning already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:14.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's my fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:15.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.72,0:20:22.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second! We just got hit \Nby Acnologia's attack and, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:23.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's everyone else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:25.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:32.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:42.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Mavis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:47.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The first master of Fairy \NTail, Mavis Vermilion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.51,0:21:02.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, I took the bond between you \Nand the faith you have in one another,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:05.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and converted it all to magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:12.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings activated Fairy Sphere, \None of the Three Great Fairy Magics.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.51,0:21:18.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Absolute Defense magic that \Nprotects the guild against all evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.39,0:21:24.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, everyone was sealed \Naway in a frozen state...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:29.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...and it took seven years to be dispelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:34.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all things... The founder protected us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.24,0:21:37.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm an astral body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.50,0:21:42.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all I could do to transform \Neveryone's power into magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:46.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unwavering faith and a \Nstrong bond between you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.21,0:21:48.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,will even win a miracle over to your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.65,0:21:52.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail has become a fine \Nguild, hasn't it, 3rd Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:21:57.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then she was gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.64,0:22:09.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten big, huh, Romeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.71,0:22:23.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Natsu-nii... Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.56,0:23:59.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven years have passed since \Nthen?! You gotta be kiddin' me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.46,0:24:02.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, it seems to be the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.12,0:24:05.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we all aged seven \Nyears without knowing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.47,0:24:08.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time stopped in the bubble, so \Nour ages are still the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.24,0:24:10.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone else is \Nseven years older, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.43,0:24:13.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So what age should we say we are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.03,0:24:16.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Seven-Year Gap
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.67,0:24:19.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just say something like, \N"I'm eternally young!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.64,0:24:21.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You expect Gramps to say that, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.85,0:24:24.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that'd be kind of a stretch.
